chat.cleanup.failure.description: There be none of th' Herobrines loaded in this here world!
chat.cleanup.failure.statement: Failed To Remove th' evil beasties!

chat.default_config.execute.statement: Successfully restored yer config to th' defaults
This here command turns on th' creeping mechanic and spawns Herobrine behind th' ol' scallywag it be executed on.
chat.sighting_summons.lurking.tutorial.d: This command turns on th' lurking mechanic and spawns Herobrine off in th' distance around th' scallywag it is executed on. Herobrine may not be spawnin' if his spawnpoint be within 40 blocks of a scallywag.
chat.sighting_summons.nightmare.tutorial: This here command turns on yer bad dreams and spawns Herobrine at the bottom of yer bunk of the scallywag it is executed on. Herobrine won't be spawnin' if the said scallywag isn't in th' bunk.
This here command turns on th' stalking mechanic and spawns Herobrine somewhere around th' scallywag it be executed on. Herobrine may not be spawnin' if his spawnpoint is be in the viewin' of another landlubber.
chat.sighting_summons.summon.tutorial.de: This command summons a Herobrine at the position of execution. Recommended for the executor to turn into spectator. A non-spectator player must be within radius.
chat.sighting_summons.tutorial.statement: Showin' ye th' ropes of th' commands
config.OGshrineMechanic.description: Toggles whether or nay ye'll see a Flash o' th' skies when lightin' yer shrine.
config.OGshrineMechanic.title: Ye Olde Shrine Mechanic
config.advancements.description: Changes whether mateys be rewarded accomplishments for From The Fog. (ACCOMPLISHMENTS GIVENS WHILE IT BE ENABLED WILL BE LOST IF YE DISABLE IT!!!)
config.advancements.title: Ye be gettin' rewarded
config.autoConfig.description: Changes if Herobrine be modifyin' the config.
config.autoConfig.title: Give away yer captain
config.burningBase.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will be tryin' ta burn down yer house once you no longer be stickin' around (there be one check per in-game day).
config.burningBase.title: He set yer hut ablaze
config.chilledCandles.description: Toggles whether or nay Herobrine can be puttin' out yer wax candles.
config.chilledCandles.title: He be puttin' out me glim
config.crashMechanic.description: Changes the jumpscare mechanic fer olde crash mechanic. [WARNIN' FER EPILEPSY] [MIGHT NOT BE RUNNIN' WELL ON YER MACHINE IF IT BE OLDE] (Only be workin' if jumpscares be on.)
config.crashMechanic.title: He be shuttin' down yer game
config.crashScreen.description: It change the crash screen texture.
config.crashScreen.title: Screens O' Crashin
config.crashScreenLibrary.progress: Config [Log O' Screens of th' Crashin]
config.crashScreenLibrary.screens.title: Screens O' Crashin
config.creepingMechanic.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will be standin' behind ye waitin' fer ye ta turn around.
config.creepingMechanic.title: Creepin' around ye
config.creepingVanishingDelay.descriptio: Changes how long it be takin' fer Herobrine ta disappear after bein' caught creepin' around near th' player.
config.creepingVanishingDelay.title: Creepin' around delay before he be vanishin'
config.crimsonCurse.description: Toggles whether or nay Herobrine be switchin' yer torches ta redstone torches and yer lanterns to spirit lanterns. (there be one check per in-game day)
config.crimsonCurse.title: He be givin' ye the Crimson Curse
config.disappearingTorches.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will be tryin' ta break yer torches once you no longer be stickin' around (there be one check per in-game day).
config.disappearingTorches.title: Yer torches be vanishin'
config.dreadfulDonation.description: Changes whether Herobrine will leave ye some booty in ye chests or nay. (Can be happenin before th' 3 days pass or if a shrine be built. It be havin' one check per in-game day.)
config.dreadfulDonation.title: He be leavin' some Terrifyin' Treasure
config.emissiveLayers.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will be havin' some glowin' skin. Useful fer players be wantin' ta make him more normal, or those that be usin' dynamic lightin'.
config.emissiveLayers.title: He be givin' off light?
config.fearfulFootsteps.description: Changes whether or nay Herobrine be runnin' up behind ye, makin' some noises.
config.fearfulFootsteps.title: He be makin' footsteps
config.ghostDoors.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine be openin' yer doors.
config.ghostDoors.title: Messin' with yer doors
config.ghostMinecarts.description: It make th' Minecarts wanna move on they own, so ye stay off th' tracks. (There be one check per in-game day)
config.ghostMinecarts.title: Ghastly ol' Minecarts
config.ghostMiner.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine be minin' next ta ye in yer strip mines.
config.ghostMiner.title: Harvestin' yer stuffs
config.hauntingDelay.description: Change up th' delay fer how long it be takin' fer Herobrine ta start hauntin' ye! (in-game days).
config.hauntingDelay.title: How many days it be takin'
config.herobrineSkin.description: Changes what Herobrine be wearin' while he be messin' with ye.
config.herobrineSkin.title: What kind o' clothes he be wearin'
config.hittingThatGriddyConfig.descripti: Changes whether or nay Herobrine be spawnin' hittin' th' griddy.
config.hittingThatGriddyConfig.title: Hittin' th' ol' Griddy
config.hoeBrineReturnsConfig.description: Changes Herobrine back to Hoebrine as a reference to th' original bug that would be occurin' when ye landlubbers would see Herobrine without th' resourcepack enabled.
config.hoeBrineReturnsConfig.title: Hoebrine Returns, me hearty!
config.jumpscareMechanic.description: Enables the ability fer Herobrine ta be gettin' in yer face.
config.jumpscareMechanic.title: He gettin' in yer face
config.lurkingLanguage.description: Changes what tongues Herobrine be speakin' towards ye
config.lurkingLanguage.title: What tongue he be speakin'
config.lurkingMechanic.description: Changes whether Herobrine will be watchin' ye from afar.
config.lurkingMechanic.title: He be watchin' ye from far away
config.lurkingVanishingDelay.description: Changes how long it be takin fer Herobrine to vanish when he been caught lurkin' around th' player.
config.lurkingVanishingDelay.title: Lurkin' around ye delay
config.musicCut.description: Changes whether or nay yer melodies will suddenly halt when ye be spottin' Herobrine.
config.musicCut.title: Stoppin' th' melody
config.nameTag.description: Changes if ol' Herobrine be havin' a nametag and how it be appearin'.
config.nameTag.title: Will he be showin' his name
config.nightmareMechanic.description: Toggles whether or nay Herobrine will be appearin' at the foot of yer bunk ye be tryin' to sleep.
config.nightmareMechanic.title: He be appearin' to ye at night
config.noSleep.description: Toggles whether or not Herobrine will be keepin' ye awake. (Won't be workin' on peaceful.)
